  "text": "In [CITATION_1] , Abbaszadeh-Mir et al. presented a linear relation between the eight link errors of the machine and the six positioning errors of the setup -gathered in an array δp -on one hand and the three components of the Cartesian volumetric errors 1 at the tool center point expressed in the tool frame -written in the vector δτ -on the other hand.",
